{"article_id":"IV8J3FuIKa5eeLGS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Israel Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu took his protest of the Iran nuclear agreement to the U.S. airwaves on Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"`` This deal will both threaten us","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"and threaten our neighbors , ''","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Netanyahu said on CNN 's State of the Union .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Netanyahu ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"who also appeared on NBC 's Meet The Press and ABC 's This Week ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"the proposal will leave Iran 's nuclear infrastructure in place .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"The Israeli leader spoke","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"days after the U.S. , allies and Iran reached the framework of an agreement","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"in which the allies would reduce sanctions on Iran","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"if it gives up the means","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to make nuclear weapons .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The parties will now try to work out the details of a final agreement , with a deadline of June 30 .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"President Obama and aides said","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"diplomacy is the only alternative to military action against Iran 's nuclear program .","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"In his weekend radio address , Obama said","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"the agreement would deny Iran the plutonium and enriched uranium","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"needed","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to build a nuclear weapon .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"`` Moreover , ''","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Obama said ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` international inspectors will have unprecedented access to Iran 's nuclear program","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"because Iran will face more inspections than any other country in the world ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"If Iran cheats ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"the world will know it . ''","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"In his television appearances , Netanyahu said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"the United States and its allies should intensify economic sanctions on Iran","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"in order to force it to give up more of its nuclear program .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"He also questioned the effectiveness of inspections ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Iran has cheated in the past .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"`` I 'm not trying to kill any deal , ''","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Netanyahu said on NBC .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"`` I 'm trying to kill a bad deal . ''","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Netanyahu also said","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"the framework will lift sanctions on Iran too quickly ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"improving its economy .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"He told ABC","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that Iranian leaders will use the new money `` to pump up their terror machine worldwide . ''","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Iran , meanwhile , says","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"its nuclear program is designed for peaceful energy purposes , not weapons .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"In his radio address , Obama said","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"he is looking forward to the debate with critics over Iran .","depth":3},{"id":44,"text":"`` As president and commander in chief , I firmly believe","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"that the diplomatic option","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"- a comprehensive , long-term deal like this -","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"is by far the best option , ''","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Obama said .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"`` For the United States .","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"For our allies .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"And for the world . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":93,"right":102,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":65,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":59,"right":64,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"